{"tid":1044651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"乜撚嘢叫做文筆好?","createTime":"2019-03-03T05:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T07:37:39.000Z","uid":239081,"like":42,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0cc10de54d48f1a5c863a2f9fa1baf62adf26047","tid":1044651,"uid":239081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"喺HKEAA見到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/130352_9e287605e408912fda2021d9cc9c0549.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F130352_9e287605e408912fda2021d9cc9c0549.png&h=ca895041&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n第一，唔講我以為我睇緊中國高考文章，殘體字多到嘔。明明考緊香港考試，點解可以容忍咁撚多殘體。<br />\n第二，文筆冗贅，乜嘢叫「在這個傍晚於百忙之中好不容易得到閒暇的我」，呢句濫將主謂結構轉為偏正結構。<br />\n淨係睇咗第一段已經唔想睇落去，好難係一篇好文章。<br />\n憑咩攞5?仲要做示例?"},{"pid":"eeb3712f1e88ead040ddedf8322358527d89472e","tid":1044651,"uid":186412,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:23:03.000Z","msg":"好撚矯情做作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8c475d79c7a2d5e9c7064754fc2ce6032ea7e9","tid":1044651,"uid":21423,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:23:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2b3664705c6a564a5d74cb2e9b6a9334fbbdb24","tid":1044651,"uid":89508,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:24:30.000Z","msg":"殘體字真係好難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8ba1d10112fad93dc8a3f115889d191ff19c64","tid":1044651,"uid":11311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"中學撚會教句子結構<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66bb7202dcc2be9f32fd869b6042f9482f8177b","tid":1044651,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:25:21.000Z","msg":"OVER左囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5e8f7e1d3bf4061787229a5b5933e6e590